video_title: Resolve || DreamSMP Animatic
description:
Hi. I recommend watching "Desolate" again before you see this one so you have an idea of where I left off. I wanted someone to be able to watch all three in a row and have them link up timeline-wise.

Song this time around is "Line of Sight" by ODESZA. I had a few others I was tossing around but this is the one that stuck. I really hope you enjoy this one, these big projects are very draining. On that note, I think I'm gonna take a break from making these huge animatics...

My plan moving forward is this:

Livestreaming - In a day or so I'd like to do a livestream (at twitch.tv/late_august_) where I go over this animatic panel by panel. I think it will help me arrange my thoughts so that I can make a better process video. Coincidentally, my second item on the list is:

Process video - I said I wanted to do it and I still do, problem is that I'm not a great explainer when it comes to the creative process. I will try my best though.

Smaller projects - I have some ideas for a few DreamSMP projects that will (hopefully) take less time and will allow me to try out new styles and editing techniques

Personal projects - I know it's not what you're here for, but I've got some original ideas that I'm excited about. Hope that's not too heartbreaking.

Here's some links to socials. I'm @late_august_ on almost everything. Follow me:
Instagram - https://instagram.com/late_august_
Twitter - https://twitter.com/late_august_
